South Korea to Form Green Technology Center, President Lee Says

-- B y   S a n g i m   H a n
-- 
2011-06-20T00:40:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-20/south-korea-to-form-green-technology-center-president-lee-says.html
South Korean President  Lee Myung Bak 
said the government will form a “green technology” center to
study technology related to energy, information technology,
environment, and to share that knowledges with other emerging
nations.  He made the comment in a forum in Seoul today with OECD
Secretary-General Angel Gurria in attendance.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sangim Han in Seoul at 
 sihan@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kyung Bok Cho at 
 kcho7@bloomberg.net  